Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.97,0:01:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.22,0:01:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面的家伙们说要交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.25,0:01:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.51,0:01:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到你们那边去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说好了 别开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.73,0:01:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手放在头上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.51,0:01:53.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有什么可疑的动作就开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.58,0:01:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.74,0:02:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.67,0:02:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是位可以信任的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.10,0:02:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能想个办法见到我爱人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.52,0:02:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果去了 不知道会遇到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.87,0:02:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在军部被反布拉德雷派掌握的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.80,0:02:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不能排除
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请再忍耐一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然说不承认真理？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.68,0:03:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你以为你集合了人柱就赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可没那么容易让你用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽说些没用的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能站起来吗 要逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们可跑不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们已经在我肚子里了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.58,0:03:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位大人还是父亲就在这里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.06,0:03:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在马斯坦古君在父亲大人那里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.66,0:03:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是完好无损就不能保证了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豆丁女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.23,0:04:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的全身眼球的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是长生不老吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:11.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不否认吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:14.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个归我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人是办不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我有炼丹术
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼丹术确实在炼金术被封印的时候也能用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个小的人造人就交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得真简单呢 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:49.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强制打开了大佐的门？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:52.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能用那种方法的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么一直以来没有干
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:04:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在把我卷入炼成中的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说了“本不想用这招 不过也是没办法”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 对他们来讲风险很高吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.98,0:05:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 能用炼金术
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:24.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来都用黑影子躲开的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.01,0:05:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又把我家弄坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是麻烦的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.16,0:05:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长生不老
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拿下了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙能无动作地…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.82,0:06:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.08,0:06:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.96,0:06:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是依然无法和司令部取得联系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报告
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,市内各处伊修瓦尔人出没
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在数个地方和宪兵队…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.40,0:06:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间和你们说明了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:07:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命 救命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们什么都不做 请告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个家是在这个地方没错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越来越黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大伙进展顺利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:25.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.98,0:07:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样直面死亡真是不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯粹地只有一直战斗到死的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:07:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经历 出生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人种 性别 名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.49,0:08:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不被任何东西所束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.77,0:08:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不为任何人 只是战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.55,0:08:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心情是多么畅快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于到达了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.92,0:08:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你的全力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不够
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不够
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.45,0:08:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管来毁灭我试试
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无名之人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难以置信 你脸上是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:51.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我居然会用这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到前段时间为止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.05,0:09:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己都无法想像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在考虑自己能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.59,0:10:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后想到的是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.91,0:10:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从我兄长的研究书中得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.81,0:10:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再构筑的炼成阵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底要挣扎到什么程度 人类
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.92,0:10:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去帮梅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普莱德怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.75,0:11:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安静点 霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.03,0:11:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻击很温和嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:43.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在完成你的使命之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会让我活下去？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就在这之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.94,0:11:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你们打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你个子小
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直与比自己高大的人战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:11:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与比自己小的对手战斗的经验很少
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲 如果打到你就抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.07,0:12:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.49,0:12:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的确一直和大个子战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.48,0:12:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才知道小个子的攻击模式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.89,0:12:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有动作也能炼成真是麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:20.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游戏到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该工作了 各位人柱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.30,0:13:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点去炼成阵的中心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.64,0:13:44.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.94,0:13:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.63,0:13:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我带到中心去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.94,0:13:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被吞噬的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.03,0:13:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.44,0:14:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.11,0:14:32.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们有把这个星球想像成一个生命体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 比起生命也许该说是系统
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你们人类一个人的情报量完全无法比拟的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.72,0:14:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记忆庞大的宇宙情报系统
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果打开了那扇门
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.31,0:14:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底能得到多强大的力量呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.48,0:14:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在使用各位人柱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.45,0:15:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开这道门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中心在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.49,0:15:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.24,0:15:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界的中心是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把世界弄到手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.71,0:15:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道你会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的儿子古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是从我这里出生的强欲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.49,0:15:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是你想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.38,0:16:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界的中心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.78,0:16:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.78,0:16:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,门之间相互战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.95,0:18:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相互反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.35,0:18:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝妙的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.39,0:18:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我压制这股能量就已经用尽全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用这个力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.69,0:18:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来打开这个星球的门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.73,0:19:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.79,0:20:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.94,0:20:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.91,0:20:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕娜可 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.62,0:20:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要打你一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱…德…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.99,0:21:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.90,0:21:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回应我的灵魂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.92,0:21:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.91,0:21:56.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.98,0:22:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不会再被你束缚了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.44,0:22:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你拉下地面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.04,0:22:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为我身体的一部分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.12,0:24:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,人类啊 拜倒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.04,0:24:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,将其称作神的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.56,0:24:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.25,0:24:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不承认就战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.76,0:24:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,赌上你们的荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.17,0:24:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.75,0:24:17.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.45,0:24:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第61话 吞噬神之人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.60,0:24:23.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.54,0:24:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是无依无靠之人所制造的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.27,0:00:08.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}终于找到了  全新的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:12.19,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}日月却来碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:17.66,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}我前往的地方  不是“未来”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:21.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}仅仅不停地追赶着“过去”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:27.96,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}不停地鸣响着 那过去的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:32.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}仿佛无法原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:37.89,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}差不多了吧  那厌倦搜索的脸庞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:42.56,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}丢掉心里的纠结
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.89,0:00:47.81,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雨  总有会停的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.81,0:00:53.03,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这么漫长  却如此冰冷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.03,0:00:58.32,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雨  为什么会选择我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:01:03.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}笼罩着我  真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.08,0:01:07.87,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雨  已经忘了停
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.87,0:01:13.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今天依然持续下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.09,0:01:18.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}在默默撑开的雨伞下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.64,0:01:29.90,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}接近那温暖的怀抱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.26,0:22:42.79,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur2}从那天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.79,0:22:47.05,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}就决定不再哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.59,0:22:52.60,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur2}即使承担再多的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.60,0:22:57.73,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}仍有无法原谅的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.18,0:23:01.15,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已经无法回到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.15,0:23:03.65,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那平凡的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.65,0:23:08.74,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我还没有做成任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.74,0:23:13.99,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的记忆之碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.99,0:23:19.87,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}又有一块  消逝而去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:22.88,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回望今日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.88,0:23:25.63,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想变得更坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:30.76,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}期望这个声音总有一天可以传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.76,0:23:33.14,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.14,0:23:35.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在风停止的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.85,0:23:40.56,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}仰望天空追寻着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:47.90,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}在黎明前散发的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.07,0:23:53.45,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}将会变成彩虹
